additional_info:
This theme affects all pages in the facebook.com domain.

<b>Version 2.4.4.1 is out!</b>

Changing colors:
I've comented the classes I changed in the css file, if you want to change de colors, follow the archive's comments and change the properties. The transparent backgrounds are set with RGBA and the other colors I preffer to use Hexadecimal.

<b>Changelogs: </b>

Version 2.4.4.1:
* Fixed bugs with new facebook's layout.

Version 2.4.3.2:
* Fixed bugs with new facebook's layout.

Version 2.4.4:
* Restyled main header menus (with opacity menus).

Version 2.4.3.1:
* Fixed header icons;
* Fixed minor layout bugs;

Version 2.4.3:
* Expanded timeline.

Version 2.4.2:
* Fixed conflicts;
* Modified dialigs;
* Blocked page ads [when likes a post].

Version 2.4.1:
* Modified Login Screen;

Version 2.4:
* Fixed bugs and conflicts;
* Changed links and text on "photo-viewer" window;
* Blocked ADs [facebook's ego-section] on "photo-viewer" window;

Version 2.3.4:
* Changed the "Photo-Viewer" window;
* Altered a few links.

Version 2.3.3:
* Fixed bugs and conflicts;
* New search box colors;
* Changed some links;
* Testing layouts with the photo viewer.

Version 2.3.2:
* Changed share links colors;
* Fixed conflict problems;
* Fixed links;
* Some new minor stuff.

Version 2.3.1:
* Fixed Main header and Page-Information header colors.

Version 2.3:
* Fixed some bugs;
* Added style to default page elements [links, titles, buttons, etc];
* Changed appearence of the main header's menus;
* Some new minor stuff.

Version 2.2.1 [First Release]:
* Fixed some bugs;
* Changed the chat title background when mouse is hover;
* Added some new effects;
* Page-information header now is transparent too;
* Fixed buttons images.

